text: Adele James is a British actress and screenwriter. She was born on 20 March 1995. She went to Richmond-upon-Thames College and University of Bristol. James is noted for playing Tina Mollett on the television program Casualty. In 2023 James plays Cleopatra on in Jada Pinkett Smith's Netflix Queen Cleopatra. This has caused a reaction due to the color of James' skin as many say that is wrong because they say Cleopatra's skin was not black. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:British actors Category:English television actors Category:English stage actors
